spec_data.Name: perl-Module-ScanDeps
spec_data.Description:
This module scans potential modules used by perl programs and returns a
hash reference.  Its keys are the module names as they appear in %INC (e.g.
Test/More.pm).  The values are hash references.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:32:56 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Recursively scan Perl code for dependencies
